{"tid":1522681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【前線自我增值】從呢條黑衣臥底既片睇到，長摭唔係要黎由上而下拍打，係要向前篤","createTime":"2019-08-31T14:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T15:04:42.000Z","uid":39316,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"244af92115ddce84bd93e1367920fea1180ae2f4","tid":1522681,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1684004208/posts/10212623718102922/?sfnsn=mo&amp;s=591676513&amp;vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1684004208%2Fposts%2F10212623718102922%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo%26s%3D591676513%26vh%3De&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=315fd5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1684004208/posts/10212623718102922/?sfnsn=mo&amp;s=591676513&amp;vh=e</a><br />\n<br />\n片中有幾位義士用長摭拍打，由上而下揮，一d都唔同，仲比人一野發開把摭添<br />\n<br />\n有裝備係手，都要識得用先得。<br />\n揮動既力量黎自速度同重量，長摭有布產生風阻，又重極都有個譜，你一野揮落去，同拍蚊無咩分別。有戴甲既，更加唔洗驚你。<br />\n但篤呢，就唔同講法。<br />\n<br />\n慣用手揸摭把，另一隻揸實摭身，唔好揸咁出<br />\n將個身傾前/衝前，順勢一野篤出去，由下而上又得，水平都得，好撚痛架<br />\n就算有甲，都感受到你個集中一點既力，唔整親都會比你推走/推到失平衡<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔係教你篤死人。你把摭唔係尖頭，人地又有甲，你就算真係想都篤佢唔死。<br />\n<br />\n係度講多句<br />\n感謝前線為我地出力，流血流汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5598a2156b15f78c1b64368dec829398ebc12afe","tid":1522681,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"勾腳，落地狗先最開心"},{"pid":"1d5d7f960f98ace7223fb27e64978223477c07c3","tid":1522681,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5598a2156b15f78c1b64368dec829398ebc12afe","tid":1522681,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"勾腳，落地狗先最開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"係喇，有乜理由唔勾"},{"pid":"ddbf5d44e7b14f7873aeb4ddcfb12bc44380ce0f","tid":1522681,"uid":7849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"